      <title>Like a Wake-Up Call，犹如一板醒工砖</title>
      <link>https://blognew.natt.cc/posts/2012-10-29-like-a-wake-up-call%E7%8A%B9%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%80%E6%9D%BF%E9%86%92%E5%B7%A5%E7%A0%96/</link>
